      "content": "sometimes i look in the mirror and i dont even recognize the person looking back. it feels like the real me—the one with actual dreams and energy—died a long time ago. now i'm just going through the motions. like i'm just a ghost or a walking corpse inhabiting a body that doesn't even belong to me anymore.",
